DataElement.preferredName: Government Funding Research Resource National Cancer Institute Program Code ISO21090.CD.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: A coded value specifying the organizational units within the National Cancer Insitute (NCI) (divisions, programs and offices) that provide funding. EXAMPLE(S): CTEP (Cancer Therapy Evaluation Program), DTP (Developmental Therapeutics Program), CDP (Cancer Diagnosis Program).
